settings.get_subscription_points: We are a women-owned social enterprise whose mission is to break barriers to employment and make pastry  education more accessible. We provide a free baking and pastry training program to individuals with barriers to employment in our industry. Students learn in-demand technical pastry skills, time management, teamwork, and problem-solving.  When students graduate and are ready to work in the industry, we help them apply to jobs with our hiring partners. These bakeries, dessert shops and grocery stores have all agreed to consider completion of our program as the work experience needed for an entry level job with them!

settings.classes_points: Our mission is to make pastry education accessible to all. Our yearly free baking and pastry training program creates economic opportunity for individuals with barriers to employment. Proceeds from our pastry kit subscription help fund our free training program. Our kits help you bake at home, while learning about new pastries and baking techniques!

settings.testimonial-text: My favorite time of the month is when I get the Pastry Project Kits! It’s a great subscription kit for people learning to bake and bakers that just want to make something yummy.
The kits are planned and put together so thoughtfully. The recipes are delicious and really run the gamut, and the partnerships add such a creative twist!
